245
00:35:28,047 --> 00:35:29,089
<b>Thank you.</b>

246
00:35:29,173 --> 00:35:31,592
<b>Hey, Spidey, hold on.
Bugle needs a photo.</b>

247
00:35:31,675 --> 00:35:33,552
<b>- Thank God you're okay.
