248
00:35:33,677 --> 00:35:35,637
<b>Hey. I'm the new guy.</b>

249
00:35:35,763 --> 00:35:37,014
<b>New guy?</b>

250
00:35:38,599 --> 00:35:39,600
<b>You okay?</b>

251
00:35:39,725 --> 00:35:42,853
<b>From now on, I am gonna be
taking shots of you for the Bugle.</b>

252
00:35:42,853 --> 00:35:45,773
<b>So smile. Are you smiling?
Just kidding.</b>

253
00:35:45,856 --> 00:35:48,358
<b>- They got a guy.
- Who, Parker?</b>

254
00:35:48,776 --> 00:35:53,072
<b>Yeah, look, just between you and me,
