256
00:35:55,991 --> 00:35:58,369
<b>Just... Yeah, a little chunky.</b>

257
00:35:58,702 --> 00:36:00,371
<b>Okay.</b>

258
00:36:00,996 --> 00:36:03,499
<b>But you don't have to worry about that
anymore, buddy.</b>

259
00:36:12,341 --> 00:36:13,300
<b>Dazzle me.</b>

260
00:36:21,016 --> 00:36:24,019
<b>Just something the boys in
the Ad Department and I whipped up.</b>

261
00:36:24,144 --> 00:36:27,064
