290
00:38:03,410 --> 00:38:05,371
<b>- Check out the light.
- He likes my shirt.</b>

291
00:38:05,496 --> 00:38:06,622
<b>- Hey, Betty.
- Hey, Pete.</b>

292
00:38:06,747 --> 00:38:08,624
<b>You better get in there. New guy.</b>

293
00:38:08,749 --> 00:38:11,627
<b>He's trying to sell
