294
00:38:13,087 --> 00:38:14,671
<b>Thanks.</b>

295
00:38:14,755 --> 00:38:17,800
<b>Parker. You're late, maybe too late.
Bruckner beat you to it.</b>

296
00:38:17,925 --> 00:38:19,551
<b>It's Brock, sir. Edward Brock Jr.</b>

297
00:38:19,676 --> 00:38:22,054
<b>- But I got you this.
- But he got me this.</b>

298
00:38:22,179 --> 00:38:24,556
<b>I didn't see you there.
