338
00:40:35,979 --> 00:40:38,023
<b>- For the cheerleaders.
- Right.</b>

339
00:40:38,232 --> 00:40:40,859
<b>- Hey, do I have any girlfriends?
- I don't know.</b>

340
00:40:40,984 --> 00:40:42,111
<b>You don't?</b>

341
00:40:42,736 --> 00:40:45,447
<b>Hey, Bernard.
