386
00:44:35,177 --> 00:44:36,720
<b>Yeah.</b>

387
00:44:53,404 --> 00:44:56,198
<b>Isn't that that guy
from that prison break?</b>

388
00:44:56,323 --> 00:44:57,783
<b>He fits.</b>

389
00:44:57,991 --> 00:45:00,577
<b>Hey, you. Halt.</b>

390
00:45:01,328 --> 00:45:02,996
<b>Cover the back.</b>

391
00:45:06,458 --> 00:45:08,502
<b>Hon, be careful.</b>

392
00:45:57,009 --> 00:45:58,135
<b>He's in the truck.</b>

393
00:45:58,385 --> 00:46:00,345
<b>Round the front.</b>

394
00:46:13,400 --> 00:46:14,943
<b>Fire.</b>

395
00:46:39,009 --> 00:46:40,594
<b>People of the city of New York...</b>

396
00:46:40,803 --> 00:46:44,348
<b>...I am here today
because I fell 62 stories...</b>

397
00:46:44,431 --> 00:46:46,016
<b>...and someone caught me.</b>

398
00:46:46,225 --> 00:46:49,228
<b>Someone who never asks
for anything in return.</b>

399
00:46:49,353 --> 00:46:53,190
<b>Someone who doesn't even want us
to know who he is.</b>

400
00:46:53,315 --> 00:46:54,358
<b>Hey, M. J.</b>

