405
00:47:04,451 --> 00:47:05,828
<b>I've never felt better.</b>

406
00:47:05,953 --> 00:47:08,122
<b>It's a weird feeling
not knowing who you are.</b>

407
00:47:08,205 --> 00:47:11,041
<b>Bump on the head,
I'm as free as a bird.</b>

408
00:47:11,250 --> 00:47:13,544
<b>Will you bump me on the head?</b>

409
00:47:15,629 --> 00:47:17,923
<b>Hey, Pete said you're in a play.</b>

410
00:47:18,132 --> 00:47:20,843
<b>You came. You sent me flowers.</b>

411
00:47:20,968 --> 00:47:23,554
